1. Meksička hrana je veoma *mekana*. (Mexican food is very soft.)
2. *Mek* jastuk mi pomaže da lakše zaspim. (A soft pillow helps me fall asleep more easily.)
3. *Meko* srce ima svako ko voli životinje. (Anyone who loves animals has a soft heart.)
4. Ovo voće nije još dovoljno *meko* da se jede. (This fruit is not yet soft enough to eat.)
5. Deca vole igračke koje su *mekane* na dodir. (Children love toys that are soft to the touch.)
6. Udarac u stomak ga je ostavio bez *mekog* dela. (A blow to the stomach left him breathless.)
7. *Mekušac* je životinja koja ima mek oklop. (A mollusk is an animal that has a soft shell.)
8. Ovaj kolač je pre *mekan* i raspada se. (This cake is too soft and falls apart.)
9. Kada spremate meso, bitno je da ga prvo *omekšate*. (When preparing meat, it's important to tenderize it first.)
10. Krevet bi trebalo da bude dovoljno *mek* da vam pruži udoban san. (The bed should be soft enough to provide you with a comfortable sleep.)